    <h2>About the App</h2>
    <p>
    Have you just met a person and you want to know more about them? Do you struggle in a social setting and lack the ability to make conversation? Well then this app is for you!
    Find out everything about a person with just a wave of your phone. Using the SCALE app, determine their intelligence, attractiveness, health and many more things that it's 
    none of your business to know in the first place! Using this information you can skip the unnecessary chatter and jump straight into a relationship. This app uses advanced softwre 
    to retrieve the information using a single scan. It's a quick and easy proccess that takes just 5 seconds! 
    </p>
